headline: Got $200? 3 Top High-Yield Dividend Stocks to Buy Right Now
summary: The stock market has taken a little bit of a dip recently.  The silver lining of sell-offs is that dividend yields rise when stock prices fall.  Because of that, right now is a great time to lock in even higher yields on some top-notch dividend stocks.
